import { StrictMode } from 'react'
import { createRoot } from 'react-dom/client'
import { AuthProvider } from 'react-oidc-context'
import { OidcProvider, useReactOidc } from 'react-oidc-context'
import { Secure } from 'react-oidc-context'
import App from './App'

const rootElement = document.getElementById('root')
const root = createRoot(rootElement)
const oidcConfig = {
  authority: 'https://localhost:10001/',
  client_id: 'Onebill_App',
  redirect_uri: 'https://localhost:4200',
  response_type: 'code',
  loadUserInfo: true,
  filterProtocolClaims: true,
  automaticSilentRenew: true,
  metadata: {
    authorization_endpoint: `https://localhost:10001/connect/authorize`,
    token_endpoint: `https://localhost:10001/connect/token`,
  },
  scope: 'AdministrationService IdentityService BillingService TenantService',
}
root.render(
  <StrictMode>
    <OidcProvider configuration={oidcConfig}>
      <Secure>
        <App />
      </Secure>
    </OidcProvider>
  </StrictMode>
)
